Create Crime Rate by District Visualization 15


 Create Crime Rate by District Visualization( import the zebra BI Charts from the Datafile)

  1. Click on the Zebra BI Charts visualization
  2. Drag and drop DistrictName(NewChicagoDistrict) to the Category field
  3. Drag and drop CrimeRate(ChicagoCrimeData ) to the values field
  4. Drag and drop CrimeRateTargetDist(ChicagoCrimeData) to the Plan field
  5. On the Filter pane, select Top N as filter type and display top 10 First DistrictName on the visualization
  6. On the Format Pane, apply these settings: Chart Settings- switch on invert  variance colors, Title- center alignment, reduce font size to 25 and change title, Design- select Custom and change Neutral color to Blue
